    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/lib/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" />
</head>
<body id="page-top">

    <br />

    <!-- Basic features section-->
    <section class="bg-light">
        <div class="container px-5">
            <div class="row gx-5 align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-between">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
                    <br />
                    <h2 class="display-4 lh-1 mb-4">Layton Temple Tours</h2>
                    <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted mb-5 mb-lg-0">
                        Sign up to tour the grounds of the Layton Utah Temple of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-Day Saints.
                    </p>
                    <br />
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-8 col-md-6">
                    <div class="px-5 px-sm-0"><img class="img-fluid rounded-circle" src="~/img/temple.jpeg" alt="..." /></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <br /><br />

    <div class="container px-5">
        <div class="row gx-5 align-items-center justify-content-center justify-content-lg-between">
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-12">
                <br />
                <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted mb-5 mb-lg-0" style="font-size:14px;">
                    We can only add a limited number of tours at this time. They will be removing the visitors center soon so that they can complete the landscaping.
                    When the trailer is gone, we anticipate being able to talk to groups on the lawn of the church across the street or at the Morgan's backyard.
                    We are trying to facilitate as many groups as possible, so please only sign-up when you can commit to coming on the selected date and time.
                    We have a lot of last minute cancelations.
                </p>
                <br />
                <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted" style="font-size:14px;">
                    We can do groups on Saturday, please text me at 801-628-4488.
                </p>

                <h5 class="display-8 lh-1">General Instructions:</h5>
                <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted" style="font-size:14px;">
                    <ul class="lead fw-normal text-muted" style="font-size:14px;">
                        <li>
                            Park on Rosewood (west side of the temple) and meet at the Visitors Center trailer.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Dress casual, except on Sunday
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>


                <h5 class="display-8 lh-1">Special Accomodations:</h5>
                <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted" style="font-size:14px;">
                    <ul class="lead fw-normal text-muted" style="font-size:14px;">
                        <li>
                            Spanish-speaking tours are available, by request.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>


                <h5 class="display-8 lh-1">Available Tours:</h5>
                <p class="lead fw-normal text-muted" style="font-size:14px;">
                    <ul class="lead fw-normal text-muted" style="font-size:14px;">
                        <li>
                            Tour (Outdoor): We will walk on the sidewalk along Oak Hills and on Rosewood in front of the temple on
                            uneven surfaces; please wear sturdy shoes
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Trailer Tour: On Sunday. Masks are required
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </p>


                <h5 class="display-8 lh-1">Please call or text 801-628-4488 with questions or special requests.</h5>


                <br />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <br />


    <a class="btn btn-outline-light py-3 px-4 rounded-pill" style="background-color: black;" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="AppointmentSelection">Sign Up</a>


